title: [SURF] a Fly In The Champagne (2009)
description:
A Fly in the Champagne is the most talked about and anticipated video of the year is about to come out. Despite hectic schedules, preconceived notions, and the most heated rivalry in modern surf history, somehow it all came together. The end result was a ten day purge of feelings, emotional baggage, dispelling rumors, talking it out and burying the hatchet once and for all. Oh did we mention the waves were going off ! Bear witness and watch rivals become friends.


Codec: H.264 MP4
Res: 720 x 480
